```

Each action: `{module, action, parameters:[{name, value, type}], modifiers?:[...]}`. `module` is a single identifier: `ui.render` тЖТ `{"module":"ui","action":"render"}`, never `{"module":"ui.render",...}`. Omit `explanation` at High/VeryHigh; otherwise one sentence on the uncertainty. Drop confidence to Low/VeryLow when the verb doesn't really match any action you were given.

